---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about the BeyondArenal family. Local guides passionate about Costa Rica.">
  <div class="bg-[var(--color-primary)] pt-32 pb-20 text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden">
     <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
     <div class="relative z-10 container-custom">
       <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Our Story</h1>
       <p class="text-xl text-green-100">Passion for what we do, Love for where we live.</p>
     </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-slate-600">
        <p>
          BeyondArenal was born from the desire to share the authentic beauty of Costa Rica with the world. We are not just a tour operator; we are a family of locals who grew up exploring the rivers, volcanoes, and forests of La Fortuna and Pe√±as Blancas.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our founder, "Chuchi", started as a kayak guide over 10 years ago. His ability to spot wildlife and his infectious enthusiasm made every tour a unique adventure. Today, that same passion is the heart of our company.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-slate-900 font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h3>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 not-prose">
          <li class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
            <strong class="block text-xl text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2">Safety</strong>
            We never compromise your well-being. Certified equipment and rigorous standards.
          </li>
          <li class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
            <strong class="block text-xl text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2">Sustainability</strong>
            We respect nature. We minimize our impact and support conservation.
          </li>
          <li class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
            <strong class="block text-xl text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2">Authenticity</strong>
            Real experiences, away from the tourist traps. We show you the real Costa Rica.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596423736737-25e227094967?q=80&w=800" class="rounded-2xl h-64 object-cover w-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" alt="River Adventure" />
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542111108264-58e38f6d6343?q=80&w=800" class="rounded-2xl h-64 object-cover w-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 delay-75" alt="Arenal Hike" />
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066013b?q=80&w=800" class="rounded-2xl h-64 object-cover w-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 delay-150" alt="Wildlife" />
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1469854523086-cc02fe5d8800?q=80&w=800" class="rounded-2xl h-64 object-cover w-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 delay-200" alt="Transport" />
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-12 bg-slate-100 p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">10+ Years of Experience</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Thousands of happy customers can't be wrong.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
